usage: dti_metrics_tracks.pl [-thr <x>] -path <netpath> [-sd] [-cut <text_file>] <project>

Get FA and MD metrics in given tracks

Options:

-thr <x>: make a threshold of <x> to the original probtrackx image. default = 0.25
-path <netpath>: look for individual tractography at probtrack_netpath directory (see manual)
-sd: export results with standard deviation
-cut <text_file>: Process only the subjects includedin this file
<project>: Name of the project (mandatory)
